</title>
<subSubSection id="6443D1E4545B68750A506468BEA4EA65" pageId="null" pageNumber="573" type="description">
<paragraph id="EF173F0DBABABE4EC273138F754C5646" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">
5-15 cm hoch. 2 Zwiebeln vorhanden. 2 
<normalizedToken id="AE8AAC4B713322B191C021F08D001FD1" originalValue="grundständige" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">grundstaendige</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="E8D8996D9CEED01C8F4CDE776930A82A" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
vorhanden, bis 4 mm breit, auffallend 
<normalizedToken id="8FD69DB5F58E9BC8129C63774F5CAE0A" originalValue="schmäler" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">schmaeler</normalizedToken>
als die breitesten 
<normalizedToken id="956BA2945752942403A9116846BB1CF1" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
, rinnig. Unterstes Hochblatt den 
<normalizedToken id="AAB172C01058E14E134A1C414E2C0442" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
gelegentlich 
<normalizedToken id="550915D09BA88181D40FC3C70894BD6F" originalValue="überragend" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">ueberragend</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="87F092B6919307A7E2D5D54128F3586B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">
<normalizedToken id="5D58DDBB1286567D2DA1A356F8D43E12" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
5-10 
<normalizedToken id="19D3E8E8D6766F04EE8AB71D4CF7983D" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">bluetig</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="64E007EB5864CD2A1FBB1BA01D3E77A9" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
dicht und flaumig behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="81131AEF4AB079DF04D34B4ABE4ADFF9" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
1-2 cm lang, 
<emphasis id="5AF83DFF9E41EE06E54075116C54DA68" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">
stumpf, 
<normalizedToken id="78E80CCFEBAC1DFB3A3D055270236FF8" originalValue="auβerseits" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">auβerseits</normalizedToken>
behaart. Griffel zerstreut und flaumig behaart
</emphasis>
(im Gebiet nur bei dieser Art so!). - 
<normalizedToken id="3125E51BFADD899862A31CA7A839F439" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="0F03F3F97AFBF8EC65B9E539A98C59F4" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FAEC44B9B981A21E6D9E854EFC6C634B" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">
<emphasis id="8C7C7A3E4CC4D121690EC41033675F21" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="E91A55EC3361CE36B39953DEBB52CDE4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">48:</emphasis>
Ohne Herkunftsangabe des Materials (Westergaard aus Tischler 1950).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B4B2B197DF50AC6CBA7E1B9A4CC2B7FD" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">
<emphasis id="E5831BFF0090DD8B53D2C6BDD89AB87F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, selten montan. 
<normalizedToken id="BF22D9DCA8AAE51DE4A35A2DA285BEEF" originalValue="Nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
, sandige, kalkfreie und kalkhaltige 
<normalizedToken id="D429A77A8D87488E822E8A24FD715324" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="B12C395CC74CE68DF179139EC76FB6A6" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Aecker</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BEE8248962403427C7C06A0C5388970A" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">
<emphasis id="FCD6895382EA7A42F5A4A065E9672536" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="708895CFA7EA1279B60692B963F44D7C" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
vereinzelt bis Nordfrankreich, 
<normalizedToken id="897AB74FCA47CE8330E7FBDCC1297D06" originalValue="Südskandinavien" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Suedskandinavien</normalizedToken>
, Baltikum, 
<normalizedToken id="444A1C90BA25299721DB50EBA6DED901" originalValue="Südrußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="573">Suedrussland</normalizedToken>
, Kleinasien; Nordafrika. - Im Gebiet in den Gegenden mit Weinklima, selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
